allam kynnu poyerikkuva.joliyayilla, mrg udane nd,anik nthoo poole thonnunnu.
njn aagrahichathu ingane onnm aayirunnilla,padicha udane joli,nnit 2 yrs kazhinjit mrg..angeyokke orupad onnm nadannilla.
pakaran vttukarkk kadam mathram bakki..
oru makal enna reethiyil vann tholvi anallo nnu oorkkumbo vizhamam thonunnu..anik maduthu..now i am 25yrs old ,age is note a number it is a reminder ,like alarm to remember us "what is your role in the world,and what you did?"
if smbody ask me this then my answer will be "nothing,i dont know.. "
oru nalla joli kitti swanthamaay enthengilm needanam nnokke undaarunn..allam theernnu nnu thonnunnu...ann njn kanda swapnam nadakkunnu nnokke oru thonnal..shapikkappetta pole..wast...
april/may marriage nadakkm..njnn happy ano nnu anikkariyilla...ammayum achanum sherikkm oru faaram thanneyaa..in marriage kazhinj avarkk oru faaramaay jeevikkan aayrikkm vidhi..nte jeevithm ingsneyokke aayitheerumenn njn orikkalum karuthiyilla..
padikkandaarunnu nnu thonnunnu..nkil kadam varillarunnu,nkill samadanm undrunnennee,poly kazhinjappozhee enthelm jolikk pokanullathaayrunnu

Onnm nadannilla,avideyum athiyilla,WAST 

ooroonnu chindikkumbo oru psyco aayi theeruvaano nnoru thonnal..ethenkilm oru doctor ne kananm 
